/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: DATASOURCE */
/*==============================================================*/
create table DATASOURCE (
DATASOURCE varchar(20) not null,
NAME varchar(100) null,
JNDINAME varchar(100) null,
URL varchar(100) null,
"USER" varchar(50) null,
PASSWORD varchar(50) null,
DRIVERCLASSNAME varchar(100) null,
VALIDATION_QUERY varchar(50) null,
constraint PK_DATASOURCE primary key nonclustered (DATASOURCE)
)
go
